HR NO. 126 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby designate Wednesday, April 15, 2026, as Child Care
Association of Louisiana Day at the state capitol; does hereby commend childcare business
owners, early childhood educators, and support staff for their incredible efforts; and does
hereby urge all citizens of our great state to recognize licensed childcare providers for their
important work.
SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
